videos.headline: Grier connects with Jennings for 13-yard West Virginia TD
videos.description: West Virginia's Gary Jennings bounces off a defender and catches the 13-yard touchdown pass from Will Grier to go up 7-0.

videos.headline: Bowman's tipped pass leads to INT
videos.description: Red Raider quarterback Alan Bowman throws an interception on the opening drive for Texas Tech.

videos.headline: West Virginia's Brown scores 1-yard TD
videos.description: West Virginia's Leddie Brown smashes through the Texas Tech defense at the goal line to score his second rushing touchdown of the season.

videos.headline: Grier delivers 45-yard TD strike
videos.description: West Virginia goes up 21-0 after Will Grier finds Marcus Simms for a 45-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Bowman finds Wesley with 40-yard TD pass
videos.description: Texas Tech's Alan Bowman hits Antoine Wesley in stride for a 40-yard touchdown to put the Red Raiders on the board.

videos.headline: McKoy runs 38 yards for Mountaineers TD
videos.description: Kennedy McKoy navigates through the defense for 38 yards and dives for the touchdown to put the Mountaineers up 28-7.

videos.headline: Grier throws 3rd TD pass of the day
videos.description: Will Grier throws a 14-yard pass to Gary Jennings Jr. for his third touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Mountaineers' defense snatches second INT of the day
videos.description: Kenny Robinson Jr. nabs his second interception of the day for West Virginia.

videos.headline: Texas Tech fans say 'I do' on the field at halftime
videos.description: A couple exchange vows and are married during halftime of Saturday's Texas Tech game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas Tech fans say ‘I do’ on the field at halftime) 2018/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas Tech's Duffey completes his first TD pass of the day
videos.description: Texas Tech's Jett Duffey completes his first touchdown pass of the day to De'Quan Bowman.

videos.headline: Texas Tech's Wesley makes amazing 35-yard catch
videos.description: Antoine Wesley reaches around the West Virginia defender and tips the ball to himself for a 35-yard completion.

videos.headline: Texas Tech's Duffey scrambles for a 3-yard TD
videos.description: Jett Duffey decides to keep it and scramble for the touchdown to make it a one possession game.

videos.headline: Mountaineers' defense comes up with huge pick-6
videos.description: Keith Washington secures the West Virginia victory by coming up with a devastating pick-6.
